Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure Hamada's gonna\Nget the best time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:52.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess.
