Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:21.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(児童)浜田と走るの 藤沼だよ｡\N(児童)かわいそう！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fujinuma is racing Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Poor guy!
